LinkedIn premium feature for $4.99! LinkedIn Job Explorer helps you by providing full transparency on the number of people that applied to a job! Is it 102 or 902? 

To get started:
1. $4.99 for lifetime access!
2. Navigate to https://linkedin.com/jobs/collections
3. Watch the extension provide you with greater insights!

Note: Upon paying for the lifetime access or switching LinkedIn tabs, you may need to refresh the page for it to take effect. Extension will run in background.
